ality: Croatian\n\nDrazen is a dedicated and highly motivated individual, who is adaptable and loves to work in a team environment. Drazen has high work ethic and is very experienced with more than 10 years in this industry.\nNew challenges and the open sea is what excite him every time."},{"name":"Danilo Dordevic","avatar":"/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5cae705-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::67b99f80-0ef5-11f0-b11c-7fef7ba7edcf/{imageVariant}","role":"Captain","bio":"Nationality: Serbian\n\nHe is a motivated and dedicated Chef with 10 years of experience both in restaurants and on luxury motor yachts. Danilo's motivation in cooking involves meeting and exceeding clients' expectations. He is extremely organized and creative. He loves to express his refined sense of aesthetics and the presentation and composition of dishes on the plate at every meal. He loves to create new dishes that will make the charter experience for the clients memorable."},{"name":"Mihaela Karlovic","avatar":"/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5cae705-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::7f90fc70-0ef5-11f0-9a1b-4d99bab66696/{imageVariant}","role":"Captain","bio":""},{"name":"Teo Mender","avatar":"/media/media::image::a::vessel::d5cae705-fe8c-11ed-889f-43d4bb723744::assets::f414b6e0-0ef5-11f0-b9db-e15412385b09/{imageVariant}","role":"Captain","bio":"Nationality: Croatian\n\nSince early age Teo’s interests are related to sea and water sports - he is very skilful in fishing, diving, kayaking and sailing. After finishing maritime high school, he immediately started working in nautical industry maintaining and cleaning motor yachts and after, working as a skipper on a smaller motor yachts. Teo can perform assigned tasks efficiently with a positive attitude in addition to interacting with guests in a professional manner and is keen to learn and work hard."}],"pricing":{"weekPricingFrom":{"currency":"EUR","price":3300000,"displayCurrency":"EUR","displayPrice":3300000,"unit":"WEEK"},"weekPricing